---
title: Hungarian Beef Stew with Basmati Rice
description: We’ve taken the comfort of a winter stew and added seasonal summer vegetables to create a light, easy recipe that can be knocked together in just 10 minutes. Minimal washing up, minimal prep, maximum flavour - it’s a guaranteed crowd-pleaser.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hungarian-beef-stew-124e73f9-bc05367f.jpg
